{"tid":344904,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老母話同你講道理根本係嘥氣","createTime":"2017-08-02T15:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T02:11:52.000Z","uid":8534,"like":151,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"913a37ebd285ed7bb924ba542a116cf5ee4b1f27","tid":344904,"uid":8534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:13:24.000Z","msg":"「有咩唔滿意就講出嚟啦，我哋一齊好好商量」<br />\n講完之後只要你意見同佢不一，佢就會話：「得啦，你唔好再拗啦」、「我同你溝通唔到」、「你真係好反骨」、「你唔使再講」、「你唔好再撐啦」等等。<br />\n<br />\n明明好聲好氣同佢講，一講到佢唔啱聽既嘢，就擺起一副閪樣閪態度，跟住你大聲啲講嘢，佢就會話：「你冷靜啲得唔得？」、「你睇下你，咩態度？」、「你係咪想激死我搵山拜？」，明明係自己態度有問題在先，但係就從來都只會覺得係人哋錯，永遠唔會去反省自己，唔會去改。<br />\n<br />\n其實啲老母想聽既只有奉承既說話，你講乜嘢都好，只要同佢意見不一，你講幾多都係嘥氣。佢想要既係一個永遠唔會駁嘴、意見同佢一樣、永遠順晒佢意、唔會發脾氣，態度語氣要好似紀律部隊咁既一個小朋友。<br />\n<br />\n我嘗試去溝通，但係經過咁多年，我放棄啦，因為佢認為啱嘅嘢，你係冇可能改變到佢既價值觀。所謂既溝通就係有佢講冇你講，去到最後仲要你道歉，然後強迫你認同佢既價值觀。OK 你 &middot; 贏。"},{"pid":"47f27e4271d4ecb87d4f279a2d451a2ece1c06b7","tid":344904,"uid":88044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:14:51.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ed040464131058d0d37a4df227d228ab293492","tid":344904,"uid":8534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n從來唔肯聽人講嘢，自己認為啱嘅就話係真理，只要同佢意見相反嘅都係歪理，固執到冇人有。"},{"pid":"1ac11cabff315ef828caad4d7ea7c23c38efb5b7","tid":344904,"uid":88044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:33:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>I know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n從來唔肯聽人講嘢，自己認為啱嘅就話係真理，只要同佢意見相反嘅都係歪理，固執到冇人有。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日持住身分話事, 咩你聽阿媽話係理所當然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌我咁多年嚟真係冇見過老母同我認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bec7f7aa3b95a1be7dac2db3eadc7308e0fc983","tid":344904,"uid":85586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:35:02.000Z","msg":"聽完哦恩係咪算<br />\n無謂晒時間搞到自己多樣嘢煩"},{"pid":"66df32f389b1266cf2690420e4d1b22aefee8efa","tid":344904,"uid":8534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:38:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>I know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n從來唔肯聽人講嘢，自己認為啱嘅就話係真理，只要同佢意見相反嘅都係歪理，固執到冇人有。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日持住身分話事, 咩你聽阿媽話係理所當然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌我咁多年嚟真係冇見過老母同我認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一次都冇，佢自"},{"pid":"2a6062f4ed19208c42497639239474b8d7fc8736","tid":344904,"uid":22265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:53:02.000Z","msg":"我老母又係咁，真係好惡頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7b0a36a94494776f4c7fd7779dfe2c422f1da7","tid":344904,"uid":89709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:53:37.000Z","msg":"以前我老母都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢兩年唔知咩事轉死性會問下我意見 大家會溝通下<br />\n不過當然佢重有硬頸既時候啦"},{"pid":"07a7b7d889c0983e9ed6fb772a32b234cb2a51a9","tid":344904,"uid":34755,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:55:42.000Z","msg":"因為老母係女人"},{"pid":"5c3c491b86fd73b1b8096c107936082dc96c70a0","tid":344904,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re